        "timestamp": "2018-01-10 14:05:40.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nI randomly unzip two zips under features dir. There are so many equivalent common jars and files. When we are running startODL.sh, and unzipping those zips just overwriting the same files/jars over and over into /opt/opendaylight/current dir.  I think we should unzip those zip files into /opt/opendaylight/current before running build docker image, if we really want to decrease the docker image size.",
        "patchset_number": 3
